Constrained Application Protocol (CoAP)
Hop-Limit Option
2020", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC8768.html", target="_top", tooltip="The presence of Constrained Application Protocol (CoAP) proxies may lead to infinite forwarding loops, which is undesirable.  To prevent and detect such loops, this document specifies the Hop-Limit CoAP option."];
